PN,31001
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has allowed the US to
OL,7,Fstrike Iranian missile sites from
OL,8,FBritish bases as officials plan an
OL,9,Funprecedented rescue operation for UK
OL,10,Fcitizens in the Gulf.
OL,12,FHostilities in the Middle East are
OL,13,Fentering their third day, with the US
OL,14,Fand Israel continuing to strike Iran
OL,15,Ffollowing the death of Supreme Leader
OL,16,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
