FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FMore than 200,000 British nationals,
OL,7,Fincluding military personnel, are
OL,8,Fthought to be at risk in the Gulf as
OL,9,Fthe Tehran regime launches further
OL,10,Fmissiles at its neighbours.
OL,12,FLate on Sunday, the Prime Minister
OL,13,Fsaid he had agreed to a US request to
OL,14,Fuse British bases to protect UK
OL,15,Fnationals and allies in the region,
OL,16,Faccusing Iran of pursuing a "scorched
OL,17,Fearth strategy".
OL,26,@xD@]OUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FSir Keir said British forces would not
OL,7,Fbe directly involved in the strikes,
OL,8,Fand the bases would only be used for
OL,9,Fthe "specific and limited defensive
OL,10,Fpurpose" of targeting missile storage
OL,11,Fdepots and launchers being used to
OL,12,Fattack Iran's neighbours.
OL,14,FHe said: "We have taken the decision
OL,15,Fto accept this request ` to prevent
OL,16,FIran firing missiles across the
OL,17,Fregion, killing innocent civilians,
OL,18,Fputting British lives at risk, and
OL,19,Fhitting countries that have not been
OL,20,Finvolved."
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@HO]vD@JOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FIt is not clear which bases will be
OL,7,Fused, but Donald Trump has previously
OL,8,Freferred to asking to use Diego
OL,9,FGarcia, one of the Chagos Islands in
OL,10,Fthe Indian Ocean.
OL,12,FReports have also suggested the US
OL,13,Fcould use RAF Fairford in
OL,14,FGloucestershire, which can handle
OL,15,FAmerican heavy bombers.
OL,17,FSir Keir's decision followed a day of
OL,18,Fconversations with regional leaders,
OL,19,Fduring which it is understood they
OL,20,Fasked the UK to do more to protect
OL,21,Fthem from Iranian missiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister insisted the
OL,7,Fdecision was fully in line with
OL,8,Finternational law, and the Government
OL,9,Fhas published a summary of its legal
OL,10,Fposition setting out that it is acting
OL,11,Fin "collective self-defence".
OL,13,FThe UK will also continue to carry out
OL,14,Fthe defensive operations that have
OL,15,Falready seen British forces shoot down
OL,16,FIranian drones threatening northern
OL,17,FIraq and Qatar.
OL,26,@sD@DOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski
OL,7,Fcondemned the decision, saying Sir
OL,8,FKeir had jumped into "yet another
OL,9,FMiddle East illegal war", while the
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats demanded MPs be
OL,11,Fgiven a say on allowing the US to use
OL,12,FBritish bases.
OL,14,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage said the
OL,15,Fdecision was "better late than never"
OL,16,Fand described Sir Keir as "a follower,
OL,17,Fnot a leader".
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@XO]wD@NOUwD@eO]xD@[OUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Foreign Office has
OL,7,Fmounted an unprecedented operation to
OL,8,Fsupport British nationals in the
OL,9,Fregion.
OL,11,FOfficials are understood to be working
OL,12,Fon plans for potential evacuation
OL,13,Froutes should airspace in the Gulf
OL,14,Fremain closed for an extended period.
OL,16,FBritish nationals are currently being
OL,17,Fadvised to stay where they are and
OL,18,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,19,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,20,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,21,Fofficials expect to change rapidly
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772460677
OL,3,CPM lets US use UK bases to strike Iran
OL,4,Cwhile officials plan major Gulf rescue
OL,6,FThose in Bahrain, Israel, Palestine,
OL,7,FQatar and the UAE have been urged to
OL,8,Fregister their presence with the
OL,9,FForeign Office online.
OL,11,FMore than 94,000 people, mostly in the
OL,12,FUAE, have already registered their
OL,13,Fpresence.
OL,15,FThe Government has used the
OL,16,Fregistration scheme before to provide
OL,17,Furgent updates to people affected by
OL,18,Finternational crises, but it has not
OL,19,Fpreviously had to deal with so many
OL,20,Fpeople in so many different countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
